  <brief_title>A Phase 2 Study to Evaluate Efficacy and Safety of Masitinib in Non Pre-treated, Inoperable Patients With Locally Advanced/Metastatic Gastro-intestinal Stromal Tumour (GIST)</brief_title>
  <official_title>Phase 2 Study of Oral AB1010 in Non Pre-treated, Inoperable Patients With Locally Advanced/Metastatic Gastro-intestinal Stromal Tumour (GIST)</official_title>
