  <brief_summary>
    <textblock>
      The objective is to evaluate the efficacy and safety of AB1010 at 7.5 mg/kg/day in the
      treatment of non pre-treated, inoperable patients with locally advanced/metastatic GIST.
    </textblock>
  </brief_summary>
